title: CMU Neural Nets for NLP 2017 (18): Unsupervised Learning of Structure
description:
This lecture (by Graham Neubig) for CMU CS 11-747, Neural Networks for NLP (Fall 2017) covers:

* Learning Features vs. Learning Structure
* Unsupervised Learning Methods
* Design Decisions for Unsupervised Models
* Examples of Unsupervised Learning

Slides: http://phontron.com/class/nn4nlp2017/assets/slides/nn4nlp-18-unsup.pdf

Previous Video: https://youtu.be/twjlGZzUM68
Next Video: https://youtu.be/cWDt6GTOpLE

See more details of the class here: http://phontron.com/class/nn4nlp2017/
